      <title>以色列空袭庞斯叙利亚军事空调，击中大马士革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/israeli-airstrikes-pound-syrian-military-airbase-hit-damascus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军队周三在叙利亚的不同地区进行了多次空袭，包括首都大马士革，随着以色列继续降低饱受战争war的国家的军事能力，“几乎完全摧毁”了另一个主要城市的军事机场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/israeli-airstrikes-pound-syrian-military-airbase-hit-damascus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 01:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚总理安瓦尔计划延长反种植机构负责人的任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/malaysia-pm-anwar-to-retain-anti-graft-chief-azam-baki-despite-criticism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[熟悉此事的人们说，马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣（Anwar Ibrahim）有望扩大反贪婪委员会主管阿扎姆·巴基（Azam Baki）的任期，尽管非政府组织对政治家的任命程序以及政客和其他人的指控批评该机构的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/malaysia-pm-anwar-to-retain-anti-graft-chief-azam-baki-despite-criticism</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 01:00:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对印度的“朋友”莫迪的压力为26％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-piles-pressure-on-friend-modi-with-26-tariff-on-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统以对美国任何主要贸易伙伴征收的一些最高关税利率拍打印度，称他与总理纳伦德拉·莫迪（Narendra Modi）的良好联系并没有影响他的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-piles-pressure-on-friend-modi-with-26-tariff-on-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:32:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RBA认为银行对美国关税的寒冷效果有弹性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/rba-sees-banks-as-resilient-to-chilling-effect-of-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[储备银行在半年的审查中说，尽管澳大利亚的金融体系非常适合环境风暴，但美国贸易政策和国家对它们的反应可能会对全球商业投资和家庭支出产生“令人不寒而栗的影响”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/rba-sees-banks-as-resilient-to-chilling-effect-of-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁贾里德·艾萨克曼（Jared Isaacman）将前往参议院参加美国宇航局听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/billionaire-jared-isaacman-to-go-before-senate-for-nasa-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[议员们将在4月9日举行一场期待已久的唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提名开展NASA的听证会，为亿万富翁金融科技企业家贾里德·艾萨克曼（Jared Isaacman）铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/billionaire-jared-isaacman-to-go-before-senate-for-nasa-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南魅力攻势未能避免46％的特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-s-charm-offensive-fails-to-stave-off-huge-trump-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南部署了特朗普政府的攻击性攻势，削减了进口税，并发誓要购买更多的大型美国产品来保护其贸易依赖的经济，但未能避免避免白宫宣布的最大关税之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-s-charm-offensive-fails-to-stave-off-huge-trump-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:24:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国发誓要对策，因为特朗普将我们的关税提高到65％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-hikes-china-tariffs-to-at-least-54-in-blow-to-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国在与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）迄今最大的关税受到打击后发誓要进行报复，这有可能使世界上最大的经济体之间的贸易陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-hikes-china-tariffs-to-at-least-54-in-blow-to-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:22:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿尔巴内斯猛击王牌对澳大利亚的关税为“糟糕的决定”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/australia-pm-says-10-us-tariff-a-poor-decision-won-t-respond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）表示，美国宣布对澳大利亚商品的10％关税是一个“糟糕的决定”，并补充说，他不会以相互征税的方式做出回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/australia-pm-says-10-us-tariff-a-poor-decision-won-t-respond</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:54:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普征收所有人，中国的利率将飙升至50％以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在一个世纪以来对美国最陡峭的关税征收，加强了他的竞选活动，以重塑全球经济和令人不安的投资者，这些投资者将贸易战视为对美国增长的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 20:16:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸的统治军事宣布停火促进地震救济工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-04-02/man-rescued-from-rubble-in-myanmar-s-capital-but-hope-fading-of-finding-more-earthquake-survivors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼谷（AP​​）＆Mdash;缅甸统治军方周三宣布该国内战的临时停火，以促进救济工作，因为地震发生了7.7级地震，造成3,000多人丧生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-04-02/man-rescued-from-rubble-in-myanmar-s-capital-but-hope-fading-of-finding-more-earthquake-survivors</guid>
